plot: Murphy is kidnapped by a group of outlaws trying to crack the 'Fort Knox of Oxycotin.' While the survivors fight drug enhanced zombies, Murphy makes a startling discovery about his abilities.

The survivors are trapped by zombies in a golf club, but they are saved by a trio formed by Zimmerman, Janice and Henry. When they learn that Murphy is capable to walk among the zombies, they drug the survivors and kidnap Murphy. Soon they reveal their plan to break in the Mesa Pharmaceutics and bring boxes of the valuable Oxycotin. However the place is under siege of fast zombies that have used the drug. While the survivors follow the abductors, Murphy discovers new abilities.—Claudio Carvalho, Rio de Janeiro, Brazil
